I want to help people. I want to work with kids who have been hurt. I want to help families. I see this work as important.

I think good workers are kind and fair. They help people. They want to learn new things. These things are important to me, too.

I like to help people. I did not know what I wanted to do. In school, I saw people run from problems. Some used bad ways to feel good. I saw bad things happen. I got a degree in Psychology.

After school, I worked for a time. I met a friend’s son. He was scared. His parents hurt him. I wanted to help. I talked to the police. I told them about my degree. The police asked me to talk to the parents. They did not want to help the son. I saw they were bad parents.

This made me want to work with kids more. I want to help kids like him.

It is good to be fair to all people. We say people are important. But we also want everyone to be the same. I am different. I like to be myself.

In school, I showed I cared about fairness. I wore what I wanted. I spoke up against bad things. I think it is good to fight for what is right.

This paper looks at two ways to look at the problem of sleep problems: the body and the world. The body way looks at genes and health. The world way looks at how things around us, like our family and job, affect sleep. 

This paper talks about sleep problems. It looks at studies about these ways of looking at sleep. It says what is good and bad about each study.

Sleep problems can be many things. They can be a main problem or a problem caused by other things. The main sleep problems are hard to fall asleep or hard to stay asleep. They can also be problems with falling asleep at the right time. Some sleep problems are caused by other health problems.

There are two main types of sleep problems. One type is hard to fall asleep or stay asleep. The other type is having strange things happen when you sleep. These strange things can be scary or dangerous.

This paper looks at sleep problems, especially hard to fall asleep. It looks at how the body and the world cause these problems.

The body way of looking at sleep problems says that genes and how our bodies work can cause them. There are special parts in our brains that help us sleep. This study looked at mice. It found that special parts in the mice brains control sleep. When these parts are changed, the mice sleep more or less. This means that genes can cause sleep problems.

The world way of looking at sleep problems says that things around us can cause them. If a person's family or job is bad, they might have sleep problems. If a person feels stressed, they might have sleep problems.

This paper talks about three things about CAPD. First, it says what CAPD is. Next, it talks about how doctors find CAPD. It tells about signs of the problem. Last, it talks about how teachers can help kids with CAPD in school.

CAPD is a brain problem. The brain has trouble using sound. People with CAPD can hear good. But their brain has trouble understanding sound. It has trouble making words out of sounds. It has trouble hearing one sound over another.

Doctors first talked about CAPD a long time ago. They called it “auditory imperception.” They found it in kids who had trouble talking. Doctors made tests to help find CAPD.

CAPD can cause many problems. People with CAPD may not hear sounds well. They may have trouble telling sounds apart. They may not hear words in the right order. 

To find CAPD, doctors look at how people listen. They give them tests. There are many tests for CAPD. There is no one test that works best.

The play Twelfth Night shows that hiding can be help full. But it can be bad for a person. A person must be true to them self. If they hide too long, they can lose them self.  Hiding can make people sad.  

Some people will not like to know they were tricked. Others will be angry.  It is hard to tell who will be sad or angry.

Changing how you look, like a man or a woman, is a big problem. Why do people want to hide who they are? In the play, Viola hides to be safe. She is in a new place.  She wants to be safe from bad men.  

Viola hides well. But she loses friends. She is alone. 

Olivia thinks Viola is a man. Olivia loves Viola. 

Orsino also wants to be with Viola. This is hard for Viola.

Twelfth Night shows how hiding can make people feel things they do not know. Maybe Olivia likes women.  Maybe Orsino wants to be with Viola. We do not know.

Olivia likes Viola/Cesario. But she also likes Sebastian. Olivia likes people who look good.

German people rule in Africa was bad. They hurt many people. This is true for the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. This rule was not always bad. German rule was different in different places.

Schools were also good in some places and bad in others. When Britain took over German East Africa, many people could read. This was good. German schools in other places were also good.

South West Africa was different. The German people did not make many schools. They let churches make schools. The government did help some. But the government helped white people more.

This made a big difference. Many people in South West Africa could not read. This was bad.

This paper looks at why South West Africa was different. It looks at the people who lived there and what the government did. 

Many people have written about schools in German Africa. They wrote in German and English. 

One book looks at schools in South West Africa and East Africa. The book says that South West Africa had many white people. This is why schools were different there.


South West Africa was not very hot. Many white people lived there. There were more white people in South West Africa than in any other German place.

Popular music has many kinds. Some kinds are rock, rap, country, jazz, and folk.  Most kinds have many smaller kinds. Heavy metal is one kind. It is strong and loud.  

Heavy metal is about many things. Some are sad or dark.  Many small kinds of heavy metal exist now. People make new kinds all the time. 

Heavy metal is old. It began forty years ago.  It is hard to say what heavy metal is now. It is like a big family. All the kinds are related. 

Heavy metal is loud music. It has strong drums and guitars. People play the music well. Heavy metal is also about strong feelings. Sometimes these feelings are dark.


Heavy metal started with drugs. Drugs made people feel strange. They made strange music.  Heavy metal music is different. It is not like other music. It is dark and strong.


The Beatles made a song called "Helter Skelter." It is loud and dark. Some people say it is the first heavy metal song.  The Beatles wanted to be as strong as the Rolling Stones.

Long time ago, the Surrealist art look new. But Henri Rousseau made art like a dream. His art was not like the other artists. He made art that was his own.

He had a dream.  He wanted people to like his art. He wanted to be famous. But it was hard. The art world was hard to join. Some people told Rousseau to make art like other artists.  They said he should copy them. But Rousseau wanted to make art that was new.  

Rousseau was born in France. He did not go to art school. He worked for the government. He had a hard life. His wife died. He had many child that died.

Rousseau liked to paint. He liked to paint what he knew. He wanted to show the world what it was like to be a simple man.

He wanted to be a famous artist. He wanted to show his art in a big place called the Salon. But he was different from the other artists.

Rousseau was like a child. He liked to paint happy things. But the art world was not happy with his art. They said his art was not good enough.

Many good think say that good things and good art are close. They say truth and beauty are the same. I think this is true. John Keats said, "Beauty is truth, truth beauty. That is all You know on earth, and all you need to know." We learn many things in school and life. But we know good things and good art without being told. Good things and good art try to show us what is good, not tell us how to be good. We study art and good things to know why art is good or why something is right. We do not make rules for making good art or good things.

We can not fully say what is good or what is good art. We can talk about art like the Mona Lisa. We can talk about the colors and the things in the picture. But we can not say why it is good art. When we like a picture or story, we say, "There is something about it." We can not say more. I think art and good things can not be fully explained. Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can not be said any other way." No matter how much we talk about a story, there is something more. I think good things and art have this thing. It is special. It is why we like them.

I think good things and art are close. We feel them deep inside. They make us feel things we can not explain. This is true for stories. Stories have good things in them. Stories are important because they show us good things.

Germany is a strong country. It has one good culture. This culture is in many places. It is from the high mountains of München to the sea city of Kiel. It is also in Köln by the Rhine River. And it is in Dresden, a city on the Elbe River. 

Germany's culture is different. It comes from many groups of people.  Germany is the land of the Germans. The name "Germany" has a long story.

The writer Tacitus said the name came from a group of Germans called the Tungrians. They were known as Germans before they went across the Rhine River and fought the Gauls.  

Julius Caesar first used the word "Germanus." He used it in his writing about the wars with the Gauls. He used it to show the difference between the Gauls and the Germans. Caesar heard the word from the Gauls.

Some people say "Germany" comes from a spear used by the Germans. Others say it comes from an old word meaning "to shout."

The writer Tacitus said the Germans were the first people in their land. He did not think they mixed with other people. He said, "Who would leave good lands for Germany?"

The Romans fought the Germans. But they did not want to live there. They took things from Germany and fought there.

Look down. See what is there. Mind see the view. Mind is quiet. Mind study the view. Mind think fast. Mind think no thought. Mind see only what is.

Long ago, artist say, buy book. Book name is "New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." Want to draw since small. Book teach how to draw. Book teach how brain see lines. Book say put box around picture. Make big picture small.

Now, look at bowl. Mind see bowl. Mind see table. Mind see room. Mind see much. Mind want to put box. Mind see only bowl. Mind see brown.

Artist see world in colors. My world is brown. This is my art. This is my story.

Hand touch the tool. Muscles move. Hand make shape. This is art? This is good?

Water move slow. Matter fall away.

Hand move fast. Hand hit the bowl. Brown thing stick.

Wear tie. Mop in hand. Look at brown thing. Bad thing. Not good.

Flush again. Think. Then, take paper. Wrap paper around hand.

Stand up. Go down. Hand go in bowl. Like mother in oven.

Teen drivers die in many car crashes. Many things make this a big problem. The National Institutes of Health say teen brains are not ready for driving. Teens also have little driving experience. This causes more crashes. It causes more rolls, fast driving, and cars going off the road. 

Teens are more likely to have crashes with friends in the car. The Southern California Injury Prevention Research Center did a study. The study showed that more friends in the car means more crashes.

Some states try to make teen driving safer. They use special licenses. These licenses have rules about when teens can drive and who can be in the car.

These licenses are not good enough. Teens are not ready to drive. Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young. He says teens like to take risks. They like the feeling. It is good to wait until teens are older to drive. If we do not wait, many teens will die in crashes.

Soon, many more teens will be able to drive. We need new laws. The laws can make driving safer for teens. Schools can teach teens about driving. No one under 18 can drive. Teens can get a special permit before they get a driver's license. They also need to practice driving with an adult.

Many states have rules about how much teens need to practice. We can use these rules for all states. This will make driving safer for everyone.

I look at old films from the Library of Congress. I see fifteen trick films. These films are from 1895 to 1901. Trick films use editing to make things look strange. I look at the way they are made. I see how they change over time.

Most trick films are made in a room. There is no camera movement. The camera stays in one place. The shots are long or medium. Each shot is one film.

The films use a front stage. The camera does not move. This is like a theater. Actors move side to side. They do not go toward or away from the camera. For example, look at the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel." The actors move back and forth.

The camera does not use close-ups. The audience sees the whole thing. This is like theater.

Most trick films are short. They are one idea. They show magic, tricks, or things that disappear.

A trick film can use many shots to make one idea. Look at "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots." It is one idea. But it uses many shots to make it.

John Taylor was a man who liked the idea of freedom. He worked on a farm and was in politics for a short time. He liked the idea of people having the power to make their own choices.

Taylor thought that farming was the best job. He liked the idea of people owning their own land. He thought the government should help farmers. He wanted the government to be small.

Taylor thought the new country had a good chance to be fair. He thought people should have the right to own things and be free. He did not want the government to take away people's rights.

Taylor thought people are good and bad. He thought the government should help keep people good. He did not want the government to be too big. He thought the government should be simple. He wanted the government to follow what the people who made the laws wanted.

Figure 17 shows a big drop in commuter logs in the third month. This was sad. We do not know why this happened.

Winter came to the college. Fewer people walked or rode bikes. This may be part of the reason for the drop. December is the end of the fall school time. Students work hard to finish school. They may not have time for the logs. December is also a busy time for holidays. Students and teachers have time off. They may not come to school.

Classes start again in late January. This may be why there were few logs in January. But we do not know why there were few logs in February.

New projects often have a lot of energy at first. This energy may go down over time. We made a special week for carpooling in March. This helped people to use the logs more.

One problem is keeping people interested in the project. Holidays and breaks make this hard. Another problem is that people like to drive. It is part of our culture. We must give people good reasons to use other ways to get to school.

We gave away prizes. We gave gift cards to stores. It would be good to see if bigger prizes would help. We could give away a bike, a car, or an electric car.

The prizes did not change during the project. It would be good to make the prizes better over time. Gift cards were good at first, but bigger prizes later might have helped.

An ETF is like a box of stocks. You can buy it easy, like you buy a single stock. It has many stocks inside. This is good. It is like having many stocks, not just one. 

ETFs cost less to own than some boxes of stocks. You must pay a small fee each time you buy or sell an ETF. ETFs have many kinds. You can find one for many things.

The good thing is to look close at the stocks inside. Make sure the stocks are good. The top ten stocks in one ETF are very important. They have most of the money.

We look at these ten stocks to see if they are good. We use math to see how much they make. We also look at how much risk they have.  

We see that the ten stocks can make more money than the ETF. They also have less risk. But we need to check if this is really true. We need to use more math to be sure.

Poe is a good writer. He wrote a poem named "Dream-Land". In this poem, Poe use the word "Thule". This word is from a writer named Virgil. Virgil wrote about an island far away. Some people think Poe copied a poem from another writer named Goethe.

Goethe wrote a long story called "Faust". One part of "Faust" is a short poem called "The King of Thule". This poem is about a sad king. His wife dies. He is very sad. He drinks too much. He then die.

Poe's poem "Dream-Land" is like "The King of Thule". The king in Goethe's poem and the speaker in Poe's poem are sad and alone. 

Poe liked Goethe's work. Poe also liked another writer named Tennyson.

A man named Rich Wayne work at a store. He tell the store boss, Paul Martin, about a spill. The spill was applesauce. It was in a road where people walk.  Martin say he have to eat. He say he no time to help.

Another worker, Mary Haddigan, tell Martin about the spill again. Martin say the same thing. Later, a customer, Jennifer Palmer, fall on the spill. She hurt her back.

Palmer say Martin should have clean the spill. She say he know the spill bad. Other people fall on spills before. Palmer say Martin did not care about people.

In California, a person can ask for more money if a boss act bad. The boss must do bad things on purpose. Or, the boss must not care if people get hurt.

The judge will look at the facts. The judge will see if Martin was bad.  If so, Palmer can get more money.

Four years ago, I took an Islam class at CBC. We talk much about if Islam is bad. This is even more big now. After 9/11, news showed Islam as bad. Now, news show Islam as good. We could not have a president named Barack Obama in 2001. He is Muslim.

The life of Muhammad is very good. But it is different from what I know. I thought Muhammad took over tribes and made them Muslim by force. But the book say he was nice. People came to him on their own.

Jesus and Muhammad are alike. They each do good things. Muhammad made food for many men. The book wants us to see Muhammad as good. It lessens the good things Jesus did. 

The book has many stories of people who became Muslim. But the stories come from other people. This is not good proof.

The book says Muhammad is good and kind. But history say he was not. I wonder if Muslims know the real story.

Jesus teach how to live. His ideas change after he die.  People think about Jesus in new ways. The world is changing fast.  

Some people like old ideas. Many people want new ideas.  People will learn more about Jesus. They will want to know his true ideas. This take time. But it will happen. People will go back to Jesus' ideas.

People will learn about Jesus. They will take away old ideas. This is like a clock going back. People will only think about Jesus' ideas.  This will be big. Many people will follow Jesus' way.

Many kinds of churches now. But later, churches will be more alike.  History has big changes. For example, people hurt Christians. Then, Christians became strong.  

The church will be strong. But the church will change. There will be less difference between churches.  People will read Jesus' words in new ways.

Before Jesus, there was Judaism. Judaism had one God. People believed in Jewish books. Many people had different ideas.

The book *The Jungle* show how people are greedy. They want good life for them. They not help others. 

The bosses of the big factories are bad. They want big factories. They not care about people. They not care about the air or the river. *The Jungle* write, "The line of the buildings stood clear-cut and black against the sky; here and there out of the mass rose the great chimneys, with the river of smoke streaming away to the end of the world." The smoke make the air bad.

The bosses not care about workers. They want more money. They work workers hard. They fire workers when they want. Workers have no good job.

Workers have no help. There are no laws to help them. The bosses can do what they want. The workers are like slaves. *The Jungle* say, "Here is a population, low-class and mostly foreign, hanging always on the verge of starvation and dependent for its opportunities of life upon the whim of men every bit as brutal and unscrupulous as the old-time slave drivers; under such circumstances, immorality is exactly as inevitable, and as prevalent, as it is under the system of chattel slavery."

Many writers use ways to make readers feel a way about things. Some ways work well. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many ways in his book *The Great Gatsby*.  He uses words in new ways to make things seem special. He also uses things to mean more than they do. Fitzgerald uses colors for this. He uses gold, green, white/gray, and red/pink. In *The Great Gatsby*, Fitzgerald gives meaning to white/gray and red/pink. He uses these colors to make readers think of feelings. 

White/gray means the same thing over and over. White is nice. Gray is old and faded. Fitzgerald shows this at the start of the book. Daisy and Jordan are always in white. Nick wears white to Gatsby's party. Tom wears a white shirt. Catherine is pale white. The only time people are not in white is when Nick is at Gatsby's party. The colors there are bright. Fitzgerald shows white/gray in small things, too. Nick goes down white streets. Gatsby's party guests are gray names. Catherine lives in a white building. Fitzgerald also uses white/gray for normal people and places. Daisy and Jordan had a white childhood. Cars and land are gray.  

After Fitzgerald tells us about white/gray, he uses them for special things. He uses these colors to show us that something is not important. This starts with Daisy.  After a long time, Fitzgerald describes Daisy in white. She is in a white car. Now, readers see Daisy as less important. She is just something Gatsby wants. Fitzgerald uses white/gray more around Daisy to show this. Her fur is a gray haze. She wears a white dress.

San Diego is good for farms. The weather is warm and sunny. Many farms grow fruits and vegetables. Many people in San Diego want food from farms that use no bad chemicals. These farms are called organic farms. Some organic farms give tours. People can walk, look at birds, and learn about farming. This can be good for the farmer.

Organic farming is good for birds and plants. It does not use bad chemicals. But organic farming is hard work. It takes more time and money.

This story is about a farm near a town called Potrero. This farm is in a special area. It has many plants and animals. Some are rare. The land was used for farms a long time ago.

I looked at a real farm near Potrero. I looked at how the government can help farmers. I want to show how a farmer can grow food and help animals at the same time.

Culture is big in talks. Culture is not easy to show. It is not the same for all people. It is not one thing. We must not say things like "all Russians are strong" or "all Japanese are good." These are not true.

It is good to know about a culture. But it is better to know how the culture will help or hurt talks. When we meet new people, we see them like our own people. We make ideas like our own.

To know a new culture, we can look at its past. We can see its good and bad parts. We must not say a culture is wrong. We must use it to help us talk.

Culture is not only about countries. Companies have their own culture. Some use long days. Some use short days. We can see culture in how people dress, how they talk, and how they find new people to work. Some companies give money to help people. Other companies only give to special places.

Culture is different in every country. Some seem the same, but they are not.

Values are very important. They show why people do things. If a culture values being polite, people will not be mean to be strong. If they value making a good deal, they will not give up too soon.

Before talks, we must learn about the other people. This will help us talk better.

The smart person say, "God is here." This is in the Bible, book of Psalms. The man Anselm use this idea to talk about God. The man Aquinas also think there is God. They want to show that God is real.  We think they are both right. We look at their ideas to see which is better.

Anselm say we know God is real by thinking. God is in our mind. We can not think of God not being. Anselm say we find God inside us. We do not need other things to show us God is real. This is called faith.

Aquinas say we can know God by thinking and seeing things. We do not need faith. This is good for telling people about God. They can think about it and see God is real. Aquinas give five reasons why God is real. He say that God is needed. Like a puzzle, if one piece is missing, we know it is there.

Long time ago, a prince was born. This prince later became Buddha. Buddha left his life. He found peace. His ideas made Buddhism. Buddhism is old. It is over two thousand five hundred years old. Buddhism is not same today as when Buddha lived. This can be seen in Sri Lanka. People in Sri Lanka have a big water ceremony. Monks and normal people do this. This is a religious thing. But Buddha did not talk about this.  Buddhism has changed. 

There are many ways to talk about Buddhism. We will use some words. 

* **Inside:** This means things that happen inside Buddhism. 
* **Outside:** This means things that happen outside Buddhism. 
* **Bad:** This means things that hurt Buddhism. 
* **Good:** This means things that help Buddhism.

First, we must talk about the ideas of Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three things: Buddha, Dhamma, and Sangha. Dhamma is the words of Buddha. 

Buddha said: life is hard. We want things too much. This makes us sad. We must let go of things. This will make us free.

There are rules for monks and normal people. These rules help us to be good. The most important idea in Buddhism is: life is hard, but we can end our suffering.

The United States and Mexico had a big fight for many years. This fight was for 57 years. It started in 1836 and stopped in 1893. The biggest fight was the Mexican-American War. This war was from 1846 to 1848. The United States won the war. The United States took Texas and the Southwest.

Many other fights happened.  They stopped just before World War One. The fight started because Americans and Mexicans had different ideas about religion, culture, and how to live. They also wanted different things. This is like other fights between neighbors.

Countries that live next to each other often fight. They have different wants and needs. The United States and Mexico are like other countries that fight. David M. Pletcher said that the United States has long problems with Mexico and Cuba. These countries are close to the United States and have fought with it. Other Latin American countries have been friends with the United States.

Religion caused problems between the United States and Mexico. This is like problems between other countries. Sally Frahm said that Americans fought against Catholicism in the past. They also fought against monarchy.  

The United States and Mexico did not trust each other. This came from their past. The English and Spanish did not trust each other. This made it hard for the United States and Mexico to be friends.

The United States and Mexico had many fights. Most fights were over land. Bandits also caused problems. They came from the United States into Mexico.

The fight stopped because Mexico needed the United States. The United States wanted to help Mexico’s money, not take more land.

Fifteen years ago, I got sick. I could not work. I was a nurse. I liked helping people. I did not choose this job because it was easy. I chose it for safety. I thought I would always have work. My dream was to be a scientist. I also wanted to be a writer.

But I was sick. I am still sick. I am 46 years old. I have no money. I get help from my family and friends.  Every day is hard. I am not safe. I am not strong.

I need help. We all need help sometimes. Bad things happen. We cannot always be strong. We need to help each other.

The government is not always good. We need to trust each other. We need to be kind to each other.

People in America like to talk about being strong. But our country was built by people who helped each other. They shared food and help.

Be ready for bad things. Have food and water. Have tools. But also, be friends with your neighbors.

Why do living things change over time? Are there rules that make them change in a certain way? In 1917, a man named D’Arcy Thompson said that we do not know how to use math to describe even simple living things. This is still true today.

Recently, people have used math to study how the parts inside shells change over time. Our study looks at how math can help us understand how shells change. We use pictures of shells to find numbers that show how shells are shaped. We put these numbers into a computer program.

We make new shell shapes with the computer. This helps us see what shapes are possible. We also study real shells to learn how they change over time.

A shell is like a tube that grows in a circle. This circle is called a whorl. The whorls are on top of each other. The center line of the shell is called the columella.

The whorls can grow at different speeds. A line between the whorls is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the last one. The top part of the shell is the spire. The bottom part is the base. The animal lives inside the shell and comes out through a hole called the aperture.

We can look at shells from different angles. The most common view is with the aperture facing us and the spire at the top.

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top. We draw a line to divide the shell in half. Then we count the whorls from the line.

We can think of a shell as a series of holes that grow over time. The holes are the apertures. We can use math to track the path of the apertures.

We can make a math model of the shell. This model can help us change the shape of the shell.

Indonesia has a problem. Many babies and young kids die each year. This has not changed much in the last ten years. Indonesia is good at some things, like clean water and toilets. But not at keeping babies and moms healthy. 

Indonesia wants to help more moms and babies. More moms now have helpers at births. But some helpers are not doctors. These helpers can not help if a birth is bad.  Many moms die because of bleeding.  

Fewer kids are seeing doctors for sicknesses.  We do not know much about how moms are cared for after they have babies, but it is a problem.  

In cities, many babies are born with doctors. But in the country, few babies see a doctor at birth. This is not fair. Poor people have less help. They can not pay for doctors. 

We need to help more moms and babies. Should we have special programs? Or, should we make the whole health system better? Special programs are good because they can be quick. But, they can cause problems.

Sometimes, special programs take too much money. This means other parts of healthcare get less money. People also work only on the special programs.

Special programs can also be confusing. Many programs do the same thing. This makes work harder.

Victorian books like to show many small things. They like to talk about rich people. Two books from that time are different. They are "Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights." These books have mystery. They have strange parts. This makes the people in the story more interesting. We learn why they act the way they do. We learn how they feel.

One part from "Oliver Twist" shows this: 
"Oliver saw many strange things. He thought he was with two bad men. They were angry. He heard them talk. He was scared. Then he heard a loud noise. He saw lights. He was confused. He did not know what was going on. He felt pain, but he did not know why."

These books use mystery in dreams. In "Oliver Twist," the dreams show us what is inside Oliver. They show us his sadness. They show us that he knows bad things are happening. When Oliver is shot, he has a dream about it. He feels the pain again. He does not know who helped him. He feels sad and weak.

In "Wuthering Heights," the nights are long and scary. The main character is sad and alone.

A few years ago, I did work in a school program. I helped young students. My best subjects were English and reading. One student, Adrian, had big problems reading. He was in third or fourth grade. He read some letters well. Other letters were hard for him. This was very strange. Adrian spoke good English. He was from Mexico. His mother came to the school one day. She did not speak English. I knew a little Spanish. We talked. Then I understood. Adrian could read. He just did not know the English letters well. I do not know if I helped him much. But I hope he is doing better now. 

I tell this story about the language problem in schools. We must help students who do not speak English well. It is not always easy to see the problem. Even if a child speaks good English, reading can be hard. We all know this is a problem. So what can we do? 

For Adrian, the solution was simple. He needed help with English reading. But for other students, it is more hard. There is no one answer. We can use many things to help. We can use two languages in school. We can put students in English classes. We can have private tutors. We can have special English classes. We must use all these things!

First, we should use two languages in school. This is good for all children. Studies show that children who learn two languages do better in school. Some people worry about this. They say it is a waste of money. But this is not true. If we use two languages in all schools, all children will benefit. How can we do this? We do not need all teachers to speak two languages. That is not possible. But we can have helpers who speak two languages.

Many people learn about big ideas when they are small. Some go to church. Some go to other places to learn. Some look inside for answers. Many people take the ideas that their parents have. Some people say no to these ideas. They say there is only what they know. People try to find good ways to live. They want to find good things in the world.  

My father said his favorite bird was a cardinal. We sat on the porch. It was raining. We smoked. The rain made loud sounds. My father looked at the rain. He looked sad. He was thin. His hair was thin, too. He did not look at me. I felt alone. I was afraid. I could not talk to him about how much I would miss him.

My father died in December. He was sick for a long time. I did not want to see him die. I stayed in bed. No one called me.

The Gothic novel is old and new. This is true for the name and for what it is.  Ian Watt says this in his book *The Rise of the Gothic Novel*. Some people say the Gothic story is not good. Others say it is very good. Some say it has no deep meaning. Others say it shows great feeling.  

The first Gothic novel is *The Castle of Otranto*. Horace Walpole wrote it. It uses ideas from old and new stories. It has new ways to write. Walpole uses old stories and new ways to show nature. He calls this a Gothic story.

Gothic stories use ideas from old stories. These stories are about how people lived a long time ago. The word "Gothic" was used for many things. People thought it was old and not good. They thought new things were better.

Gothic stories are old and new. They use stories from the past. They also use new ways to tell stories. This is why Gothic stories are still read today.

One idea in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is about how knights were trained.  This idea is important in Gothic stories. Knights were brave and good. Gothic writers liked this idea. They thought people were not as brave and good now.

Gothic writers used chivalry to make the past seem better. They hoped this would make the present better. Walpole wrote *The Castle of Otranto* when things were bad in the world. He was worried about the future. He may have thought that people were not as good as they used to be.

One character in *The Castle of Otranto* is Frederic. He is a prince. He has been sad. He is supposed to be dead.

Frederic is like a knight. He is brave and kind. But he is also too good. This is a common idea in Gothic stories.

Supply chain is how we move goods.  It starts with a customer order. Then we get the things we need to make the goods. We make the goods. Then we send the goods to the customer.  

A man named Keith Oliver made up the word "supply chain" in 1982. He said it is about planning, doing, and checking how things move in the supply chain.

There are six big things in a supply chain. They are make, get, keep, put, move, and tell.  Managers use these things to help customers.

Make is the first thing.  We make things for customers. Managers must know what customers want. They look at the market to see what people want.

Managers look at the market to see what people want. Then they decide what to make and how much. They also decide where to make things. They want to make good things and meet customer wants.

Next, managers plan how much work to do and how to keep machines working.  Making things is important. If we do not plan, it costs money.

The second thing is get. This means how we get the things we need to make things. We may make some things ourselves. But we may also ask other companies to help.

We ask other companies to help because it is faster and cheaper.

This study looked at the link between a healthy diet and heart health. The diet is called the "Mediterranean Diet" or "aMed diet". This diet has lots of plants, fruit, nuts, and fish. It has less meat and fat.

Before studies showed that this diet helps people live longer. They also said it helps people lose weight. This study looked at how the diet helps people avoid heart disease and stroke.

The study followed 74,886 women. They were all nurses. The nurses answered questions about what they ate. They did this many times over 20 years.

The study found that women who ate the aMed diet had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke. They were less likely to have problems with their heart.

In two thousand seven, the United States had a big money problem. People lost jobs. Houses lost value. Many big companies had big problems. This problem is still here. We need to know: how did this happen? How can we stop it? The problem was bad choices by people in charge. They made banks give out bad loans. The banks were not strong. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac took these bad loans and made them into new things. When people could not pay back the loans, the banks had no money. This made the problem worse. This problem started in nineteen ninety-nine. President Clinton wanted to be president again. He made it easy to get loans. This made the bad loan problem worse later. A man named Steven Holmes said this would happen. He was right. Bad loans are bad.

Many things made the problem worse. New kinds of loans made things more complicated. Houses became very expensive. People borrowed too much money. When house prices went down, banks had big problems. Big banks had many bad loans. Some banks had to close. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac were in big trouble. The government had to help them.

Exposition is hard. It can be very boring. Some people like it. Some people do not.

Exposition is when you tell the reader things. It is not good to tell too much. A good story is about showing, not telling.

For example, you can say a man is kind. But you can also show he is kind by how he acts.

In a story, the man can help someone. He can give them food. He can listen to them talk. This shows he is kind.

It is good to show the reader things. It is better than telling them.

Brothers have a strong bond. This bond is like a promise. It is strong and will not go away. Brothers feel many things for each other. They feel love, pride, envy, and even meanness. Brothers know each other well. They know each other better than anyone else. When things are very bad, the true bond comes out. It can be good or bad. 

These strong feelings have a cost. To understand these feelings, we must look at what they do. When we look at our brother, we see ourselves. We see who we really are. Our actions show who we are. 

The story "The Scarlet Ibis" shows this bond. Two brothers go on a trip. They go on a trip that will not work. One brother feels very proud. The other brother feels very sad. In the end, only one brother lives. 

The story shows us how the main character feels. It also shows us how he sees the world. His feelings and his view of the world make him act in certain ways.

The main character feels pride most of all. He wants his brother to be strong. He wants to teach him things. He wants to race with him. But the brother is weak. He cannot do these things. The main character is angry and sad. He even thinks about hurting his brother. But then his brother smiles. The main character feels love for his brother.

The brain is big and strong. It takes in new things all the time. Long ago, people said the brain was like a tablet. Then they said it was like paper. Now they say it is like a computer. But the brain is different. It is more than any of these things.

The brain takes in information. It sees things, hears sounds, feels touch. It turns these things into signals. The brain uses these signals to learn. It looks for patterns. It puts things together.

For example, see a box. The brain sees the shape, the color, the edges. It knows this is a box. The brain also uses what it knows to help. It knows a box is not a hole.

The brain has a filter. It chooses what is important. It lets you see your name in a noisy room. It lets you not see every blade of grass.

The brain keeps information. We call this memory. There is short memory and long memory. Short memory is like holding a thought for a short time. Long memory keeps things for a long time.

People try to understand how the brain works. They make models. One model is like a web. Ideas are connected. Words are connected.

Aldous Huxley’s book *Brave New World* shows a bad future.  Technology and money are bad. People like to be part of a group. They want to be happy. The people in the book are not free. They must follow the rules of the World Controller. 

The book shows ideas from Karl Marx. Marx talked about how money can make people think in bad ways.  He called this “false consciousness.”  People in the book are happy to buy things. They do not see how the system is unfair.

The World Controller is like the boss of all the people.  He makes the people happy. He does this by making them buy things.  The people are not free to think for themselves. They are like machines.

People do not have real love in the book. They do not have strong feelings. They talk about people in a bad way. The people are not happy. They are just following the rules.   The book shows how bad money and rules can be.
